PrecisRe-appointment of the HONOURABLE PIERRE S. PETTIGREW, P.C., of Toronto, Ontario, as Chairperson of the Board of Directors of the Asia-Pacific Foundation of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective July 1, 2022.
